    ===============
     AQUAPLANET   
    ===============
   -->
    <desc compset="_DOCN%SOMAQP"      >CAM atmosphere in aquaplanet mode: </desc>
    <desc compset="_DOCN%AQP"         >CAM atmosphere in aquaplanet mode with prescribed-SST: </desc>
